Interface GameEvent

All Superinterfaces:
Holder<GameEvent>, Keyed, RegistryKey<GameEvent>, StaticProtocolObject<GameEvent>
public sealed interface GameEvent extends StaticProtocolObject<GameEvent>
Represents a game event. Used for a wide variety of events, from weather to bed use to game mode to demo messages.
